  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COOPRITU  vers une cooperative professionnelle</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Achat de   2 balance plate-forme
       Achat de 1 Humidim&#xE8;tre &#xE0; grain 
       &#xC9;coles champs paysan et pratique de la Gestion Integr&#xE9;e de la Fertilit&#xE9; des Sols (GIFS)
       S&#xE9;ances d&apos;information des membres du contrat   riz et campagnes de mobilisation   des non-membres &#xE0; rejoindre la cooperative. 
       R&#xE9;vision du MAPAF   (manuel de procedures administratives et financi&#xE8;res) 
       Achat d&apos;un modem   pour acces internet + frais mensuel de communication et achat Microsoft   Office + papeterie bureau (+ laptop occasion d&apos;Agriterra)
       Atelier pour le d&#xE9;veloppement d&apos;un plan   strat&#xE9;gique (plan financier inclus)
       Atelier pour le d&#xE9;veloppement d&apos;un plan   d&apos;affaire (+plan de tr&#xE9;sorerie et plan des   operations)
       Am&#xE9;lioration de la comptabilit&#xE9; en Excel et pr&#xE9;paration des &#xE9;tats financiers
       Suivi du contrat   et des livraisons &#xE0; Bralima</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COOPRITU is one of the 5 cooperatives participating in the Ruzizi Rice Project 18at-8092.COOPRITU has 109 affiliated members and 200 potential members. Their fields are within the irrigated area of the Sange watershed  which covers an area of 289 ha of the irrigated perimeter. The members access to  storage service from the cooperative  shelling and rice marketing services. In the recent past  Coopritu has collected and delivered on the market about 100 tons per year. She hopes to reach 113 tons in the year 2019 to book at the Bralima. It intends to start from the Synergy of potential cooperatives partners of Agriterra within the framework of this project.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Coopritu would like to professionalize Rice business activities in order to improve the level of income for his member trough the selling of more quantities to bralima industry.</narrative>
  </description>
